{"title_page": "Equestrian at the 2017 Southeast Asian Games", "text_new": "{{Infobox Southeast Asian Games event\n| event         = Equestrian\n| year          = 2017\n| image         = Equestrian, KL 2017.png\n| caption       =\n| venue         = International Endurance Park<br>Putrajaya Equestrian Park\n| date          = 20\u201328 August 2017\n| competitors   =\n| nations       =\n| previous      = [[Equestrian at the 2015 Southeast Asian Games|2015]]\n| next          = [[Equestrian at the 2019 Southeast Asian Games|2019]]\n}}\n{{Equestrian at the 2017 Southeast Asian Games}}\nThe '''[[Equestrianism|equestrian]]''' competitions at the [[2017 Southeast Asian Games]] in [[Kuala Lumpur]] were held at International Endurance and Putrajaya Equestrian Park.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kualalumpur2017.com.my/seagames-sport.cshtml?cid=36|title=KL 2017: Equestrian|publisher=[[2017 Southeast Asian Games|KL 2017]]|accessdate=13 February 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170214181530/http://www.kualalumpur2017.com.my/seagames-sport.cshtml?cid=36|archive-date=14 February 2017|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\nThe 2017 Games feature competitions in six events (all events for mixed).\n\n==Events==\nThe following events will be contested:\n{|\n|\n*'''Dressage'''\n**Individual\n**Team\n*'''Endurance'''\n**Individual\n**Team\n*'''Show Jumping'''\n**Individual\n**Team\n|}\n\n===Schedule===\n\n==Participation==\n===Participating nations===\n{{div col|colwidth=22em}}\n* {{flagSEAGF|BRU|2017|}}\n* {{flagSEAGF|CAM|2017|}}\n* {{flagSEAGF|INA|2017|}}\n* {{flagSEAGF|LAO|2017|}}\n* {{flagSEAGF|MAS|2017|}}\n* {{flagSEAGF|MYA|2017|}}\n* {{flagSEAGF|PHI|2017|}}\n* {{flagSEAGF|SIN|2017|}}\n* {{flagSEAGF|THA|2017|}}\n* {{flagSEAGF|TLS|2017|}}\n* {{flagSEAGF|VIE|2017|}}\n{{div col end}}\n\n==Medal summary==\n===Medal table===\n{{Color box|#ccccff|border=darkgray}} Host nation (Malaysia)\n\n{{Medals table\n | caption        = \n | host           = \n | flag_template  = flagSEAGF\n | even